{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "6c7f7f8f-58f3-4e89-8f2c-7d5536f8e3b1",
    "name": "ECommerce Backend API",
    "description": "## Quick testing\n\n### Variables (Collection → Variables)\n- `baseUrl`, `adminEmail`, `adminPassword` (match seed admin / `.env`)\n- `customerEmail`, `customerPassword`\n- `workerEmail`, `workerPassword`, `employeeId`\n\n### Every request\n- **Pre-request**: sets `transactionId` = unique id (use in Verify Payment).\n- **Tests**: saves tokens by role (`admin`/`worker`/`customer`), plus `productId`, `orderId`, `paymentId`, `reviewId`, `companyId`, `userId`, first `notificationId` from lists.\n\n### Fast path\n1. **00 Quick Start** → Login Admin → Login Worker.\n2. **Worker** → Create Worker (if not seeded).\n3. **Product** → Create Product.\n4. **Users** → OTP → Verify OTP → Complete Registration → Login Customer.\n5. **Cart** → Add → **Order** → Create → **Payment** → Initiate → Verify (uses `{{transactionId}}`).\n\n### Collection Runner\nUse iteration delay **300–500 ms** if Mongo writes overlap. Order folders manually in Runner if needed.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:5000/api" },
    { "key": "adminEmail", "value": "admin@gmail.com" },
    { "key": "adminPassword", "value": "Admin@123" },
    { "key": "customerEmail", "value": "customer1@example.com" },
    { "key": "customerPassword", "value": "Cust@123" },
    { "key": "workerEmail", "value": "worker1@example.com" },
    { "key": "workerPassword", "value": "Worker@123" },
    { "key": "employeeId", "value": "EMP1001" },
    { "key": "transactionId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "customerToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "adminToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "workerToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "productId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "orderId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "paymentId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "reviewId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "companyId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "userId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "notificationId", "value": "" }
  ],
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "pm.collectionVariables.set('transactionId', 'TXN' + Date.now());"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "listen": "test",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "const code = pm.response.code;",
          "let data = null;",
          "try { data = pm.response.json(); } catch (e) {}",
          "const name = pm.info.requestName || '';",
          "if (code >= 200 && code < 300) {",
          "  pm.test(name + ' — HTTP ' + code, function () { pm.expect(code).to.be.within(200, 299); });",
          "} else {",
          "  pm.test(name + ' — responded (' + code + ')', function () { pm.expect(code).to.be.at.least(100); });",
          "}",
          "if (!data) return;",
          "if (data.token) {",
          "  const role = data.user && data.user.role;",
          "  if (role === 'admin') pm.collectionVariables.set('adminToken', data.token);",
          "  else if (role === 'worker') pm.collectionVariables.set('workerToken', data.token);",
          "  else if (role === 'customer') pm.collectionVariables.set('customerToken', data.token);",
          "  else if (data.userId) {",
          "    pm.collectionVariables.set('customerToken', data.token);",
          "    pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', String(data.userId));",
          "  } else {",
          "    pm.collectionVariables.set('customerToken', data.token);",
          "  }",
          "}",
          "if (data.user && data.user.id && !pm.collectionVariables.get('userId')) {",
          "  pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', String(data.user.id));",
          "}",
          "const setIf = (k, v) => { if (v) pm.collectionVariables.set(k, String(v)); };",
          "if (data.product && data.product._id) setIf('productId', data.product._id);",
          "if (data.order && data.order._id) setIf('orderId', data.order._id);",
          "if (data.payment && data.payment._id) setIf('paymentId', data.payment._id);",
          "if (data.review && data.review._id) setIf('reviewId', data.review._id);",
          "if (data.company && data.company._id) setIf('companyId', data.company._id);",
          "if (data.user && data.user._id && name.indexOf('Complete') !== -1) setIf('userId', data.user._id);",
          "if (data.worker && data.worker._id && name.indexOf('Create Worker') !== -1) setIf('userId', data.worker._id);",
          "if (Array.isArray(data.products) && data.products.length) setIf('productId', data.products[0]._id);",
          "if (Array.isArray(data.orders) && data.orders.length) setIf('orderId', data.orders[0]._id);",
          "if (Array.isArray(data.payments) && data.payments.length) setIf('paymentId', data.payments[0]._id);",
          "if (Array.isArray(data.notifications) && data.notifications.length) setIf('notificationId', data.notifications[0]._id);",
          "if (data.notification && data.notification._id) setIf('notificationId', data.notification._id);"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
